snippet.title: Amber Heard Steps Out After Marrying Johnny Depp WATCh
snippet.description:
Amber Heard keeps it chic in a black skirt while attending the unveiling of the Alice In Wonderland themed window at the Temperley Shop, Bruton Street on Friday (Februrary 20) in London, England.
The 28-year-old actress was seen holding hands with fashion designer Alice Temperley at the unveiling.

This was the first time that Amber has been spotted since getting hitched to her husband Johnny Depp on his private island earlier this month.
